    description: 'Volg leveranciers, beheer certificaten en compliance-documentatie, en plan periodieke leveranciersbeoordelingen.',
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5m.75-9l3-3 2.148 2.148A12.061 12.061 0 0116.5 7.605"></path></svg>`,
    title: 'Directiebeoordelingen',
    description: 'Gestructureerd beoordelingsproces met agendapunten, actiepunten, besluitregistratie en samenwerkingstools.',
  },
];
---

<section id="functies" class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase text-primary-600 mb-3">Alles Wat U Nodig Heeft</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-950 tracking-tight">
        Eén platform voor volledige ISO-compliance
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-primary-900/60">
        Van begeleide implementatie tot certificeringsgereedheid — Control One dekt elk aspect van uw compliance-traject.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {features.map(feature => (
        <div class="group p-6 rounded-2xl border border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-100/50 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary-50 text-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-primary-100 transition-colors">
            <Fragment set:html={feature.icon} />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-950 mb-2">{feature.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-primary-900/60 leading-relaxed">{feature.description}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
